Image Prompt:
Create an ethereal and majestic depiction of Jesus Christ in a modern setting, blending elements of traditional biblical imagery with a contemporary twist. Show Jesus in a spotlight, surrounded by a diverse group of people representing humanity, with a backdrop that fuses ancient Jerusalem with elements of a modern city skyline. Incorporate symbolic imagery like a crown of thorns, rays of light, and musical notes to convey the essence of Jesus Christ Superstar, capturing both the divine and human aspects of his character.
